      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "啊哈！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00002",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李三春上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00003",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "为人莫当家，当家乱如麻。开门七件事，柴米油盐酱醋茶。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00004",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "我李三春，配与田三为妻。他弟兄三个，大哥是一个黉门秀士，大嫂子是个吃斋念佛的人，天天念经，指望着上西天呐。我们二哥，在衙门里头当了一名头儿，我二嫂子，是个老好子，一天不多言，不多语。这个家，就是我一个人当着。这个要茶，那个要饭，今个不是靡有米，就是靡有柴。这个日子，我可是在当不了。想个什么法子，能够把这个家业分了，可就好啦。哦，有啦。待我到厨房里去，祷告我们灶王老爷子去，能够保佑着，把这个家分了。我好好地谢候谢候他。就此走走。",
      "text_length": 215
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00005",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "吹腔",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "李三春把计生，手拿着棍一根。迈步且把厨房进，一秉虔诚祷告灶君。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00006",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李三春推门。灶君、小鬼暗同上。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00007",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "嘎，你看我们灶王老爷子，浑身是土，待我给他开开光。呸，呸，我与你掸掸土，我给你磕个头。我说灶王老爷子，你要能够保佑我们，把这分家分了，我等明天，买只老母鸡，我把它煮煮，给你个鸡扒皮吃。你要是不能够保佑吓，我一天打你个七八遍。",
      "text_length": 112
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00008",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "田大上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00009",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "迈步且把后院进，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00010",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "你老人家要是保佑我们把家分了便罢，如若不然，我一天就打你个七八遍。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00011",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "三弟妹打灶君所为何情？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00012",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "哦哈。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00013",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "我说门外头是谁呀？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00014",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "是愚兄在此。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00015",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "原来大哥。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00016",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "正是。愚兄有一言，要请三弟妹到前庭言讲。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00017",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "是啦。你先走，我随后就去。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00018",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "你就要来吓。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00019",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "田大下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00020",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈，我在那刚一打你，你就把我们大哥给弄来啦。我还是那一句话，你要不保佑着我们分了家，我一天还是打你个七八遍。",
      "text_length": 55
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00021",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小鬼看。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00022",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "咳，可气死我了！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00023",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李三春捽棍，下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00024",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "灶君"
      ],
      "text": "李氏三春太不良，终朝每日打灶王。明日上殿奏一本，叫她师傅屁股眼下长大疮！",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00025",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "灶君、小鬼同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00026",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "田大、田大妻同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00027",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "读书求功名，",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00028",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "田大妻"
      ],
      "text": "拜佛念经文。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00029",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "今有三弟妹，清晨起来，打骂灶君，不知为了何事？",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00030",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大妻"
      ],
      "text": "待我唤她出来。三弟妹哪里？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00031",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "来了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00032",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李三春上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00033",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "忽听兄嫂唤，迈步到跟前。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00034",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "大哥、大嫂子。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00035",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大",
        "田大妻"
      ],
      "text": "三弟妹，清晨早起，打骂灶君，不知为了何事？",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00036",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "大哥、大嫂子有所不知，只因咱们这个日子，实实难过。我这个家，也真是当不了啦。我想要分居另过。",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00037",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "三弟妹说哪里话来。常言道得好：",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00038",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "分居不胜同居好，大家捧柴火焰高。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00039",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "张公艺九世同居，世间少有。兄有一言，你且听了：",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00040",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "三弟妹休得要闹吵吵，愚兄言来听根苗：分家不如同居好，大家捧柴火焰高。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00041",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "大哥这个话，你也不要再说啦。我的心思是一定啦。你若分给我便罢，如若不然，我就与你天天吵，天天闹。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00042",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "吓哈！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00043",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "田二上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00044",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "太爷退堂出衙道，急忙回家看根苗。一脚门里一脚门外，",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00045",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "你要是不分给我，我就与你天天吵，天天闹。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00046",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "嗐！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00047",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "又听得三弟妹乱七八糟。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00048",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "我说大哥呀，今个大清早起，你把三弟妹，弄得这么鸡毛子喊叫，到底是为的什么事下？",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00049",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "二弟，你回来了？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00050",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "我回来啦。我早就回来啦。到底三弟妹这是为什么呀？",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00051",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "三弟妹要分家。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00052",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "她要分家，你就该去劝她才是。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00053",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "愚兄再三相劝，她执意不听也是枉然。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00054",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "你是什么也不能干，你瞧我的。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00055",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "你去劝来。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00056",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "我说三弟妹，愚兄这儿有礼啦。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00057",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "罢啦，你才下学吗？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00058",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "如何？",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00059",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "你得啦！我这受着热呐！三弟妹，你可是真不对。哥哥在这与你施礼，你怎么说才下学呀？",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00060",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "今个是年下啦？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00061",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "不是呀。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00062",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "是过节？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00063",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "也不是。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00064",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "一不是年，二不是节，你作的什么揖呀？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00065",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "不错。我这叫做礼多人不怪。我且问你：大清早起，你吵吵闹闹，莫非是咱们大哥得罪你啦？",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00066",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "我们大哥，是个读书的人，他怎么会得罪着我？不是的。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00067",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "哦。是咱们大嫂子得罪着你啦？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00068",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "你说是咱们大嫂子得罪着我？你想她是个吃斋念佛的人，除了烧香，就是磕头，将来人家想上西天呐！",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00069",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "对啦，上西天，可别上冬天，冬天还靡有皮袄啦！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00070",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "不是的。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00071",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "那么莫非是我得罪你啦么？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00072",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "二哥你是衙门里头出来进去这么一个粉红头儿。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00073",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "头儿就得啦，别上颜色啦！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00074",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "你是天天不在家，你怎么也得罪不了我。不是的。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00075",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "是啦，必是你二嫂子得罪了你啦。如果是她，等我打她一顿，给你出出气。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00076",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "得啦，得啦！你别说啦！有一天我打你们房门口过，听见里头吵吵闹闹，我把窗户纸捅破了一个小窟窿一看，你给二嫂子那儿跪着呐！",
      "text_length": 59
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00077",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "你哪儿知道，我是掉在炉火坑里啦。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00078",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "我们二嫂子，还是气得呼吓呼吓地生气呐！",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00079",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "你不知道，那是我教她吹唢呐换气啦。你不生气，愚兄有一言，你且听了。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00080",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "三弟妹不必怒冲霄，细听二哥说根苗：分家不如同居好，大家捧柴火焰高。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00081",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "这几句话人家早说过了。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00082",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "哪个王八蛋说过了？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00083",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "咳！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00084",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "大哥说过啦。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00085",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "我看你是好说不成，我简直告诉你说，你不听话，二哥今个要管教管教你。我要打你！",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00086",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "好，你要打，你来罢！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00087",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "二弟万万使不得。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00088",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "你不要管，我的气上来，王八蛋也挡不住。你招打！",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00089",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李三春坐。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00090",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "我说东邻呐，西舍呀！我们当家的不在家，他们两个大伯子，在这里争风呐！好，你们来罢！",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00091",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "大哥你去罢。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00092",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "咳，不要胡说。看她既是这样吵闹，你我就将家私分与了她罢。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00093",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "好，分就分了罢。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00094",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "三弟妹不要动怒，将家私分与你就是了。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00095",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "好，分给我啦。分给我，我就不闹了。嗳呀，大哥，你回避回避。二哥，你也掉过去，我们这儿一生气，把裤腰带撑断啦。我说你们大家都看看，我但凡有一根整裤腰带，我也不分这个家。",
      "text_length": 83
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00096",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "你那是说瞎话呐。你里头不是系着花汗巾吗？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00097",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李三春"
      ],
      "text": "我们走啦。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00098",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田大"
      ],
      "text": "分了罢！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00099",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "田二"
      ],
      "text": "分了罢！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01015010_e00100",
      "play_id": "01015010",
      "scene_id": "01015010_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 100,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖牌子〗。众人同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    }
  ],
